headline: Aledade Appoints Two National Health Experts to Board of Directors
summary: BETHESDA, Md., August 28, 2025--Aledade today announced the appointment of two national health care leaders, Shawn Guertin and Joneigh S. Khaldun, M.D., to its Board of Directors.
